post_title: Wanted: Fun backed T206 Bender with Trees in VG or VGEX
post_content:
Hey all,
I’m working to upgrade some of my Piedmont backed HOFer cards to some better backs in the HOFer set.

Does anyone have a fun backed Bender With Trees that they would sell or trade? Looking for VG or VGEX.

I have a Bender Trees with a P350 back in a PSA 4.5 holder and a Bender No Trees EPDG in a SGC 3. I could trade those, my other HOFers in my other recent post, cash and trade or cash.

Let me know what you would part with. This card comes with some fun backs, so hopefully some will part with one.

Enjoy your Sunday,
Bob

I appreciate it, but I need one with the trees in the background.

Good luck with that one, it’s a real beauty!

Thanks again,
Bob
